PRI Automation shareholders approve split . PRI Automation Inc said that its shareholders have approved an increase in the company ' s authorized common shares , as required to implement a previously announced two - for - one stock split approved by its board on March 4 . The company said the split will be effected by the distribution on May 3 of a 100 percent stock dividend to shareholders of record on April 22 . The shareholders ' action has increased the number of shares of authorized common stock to 24 million , from 12 million . PRI currently has about 7 . 8 million shares outstanding . 
